itemDescription: counter-intelligence officer and magistrate, second wife of Victor Rothschild, third Baron Rothschild

wikipedia_page.main: Teresa Georgina "Tess" Rothschild, Lady Rothschild,  (née Mayor; 10 September 1915 – 29 May 1996) was a British counter-intelligence officer and magistrate. She was the second wife of Victor Rothschild, 3rd Baron Rothschild.
